<h2 style="color: #00533a; text-align: center;"><a data-udi="umb://document/74e9938fefbc44828dcfad97a456f996" href="/{localLink:umb://document/74e9938fefbc44828dcfad97a456f996}#Highlights" title="Lake Garda Highlights" data-anchor="#Highlights">Highlights</a> | <a data-udi="umb://document/74e9938fefbc44828dcfad97a456f996" href="/{localLink:umb://document/74e9938fefbc44828dcfad97a456f996}#Itinerary" title="Lake Garda Highlights" data-anchor="#Itinerary">Itinerary</a> | <a data-udi="umb://document/74e9938fefbc44828dcfad97a456f996" href="/{localLink:umb://document/74e9938fefbc44828dcfad97a456f996}#Includes" title="Lake Garda Highlights" data-anchor="#Includes">Your holiday includes</a> | <a data-udi="umb://document/74e9938fefbc44828dcfad97a456f996" href="/{localLink:umb://document/74e9938fefbc44828dcfad97a456f996}#Hotels" title="Lake Garda Highlights" data-anchor="#Hotels">Hotels</a> | <a data-udi="umb://document/74e9938fefbc44828dcfad97a456f996" href="/{localLink:umb://document/74e9938fefbc44828dcfad97a456f996}#Dates" title="Lake Garda Highlights" data-anchor="#Dates">Departure dates</a></h2>
<div style="overflow-x: auto;"></div>
<h3 style="color: #00533a;"><a name="Highlights"></a>Highlights</h3>
<ul>
<li>See the different landscapes of Italy's largest lake, from the vineyards of the south to the mountainous north</li>
<li>Enjoy time in bustling Garda and activity filled <a data-udi="umb://document/8bac09b5ee37405a9498e1494235fa01" href="/{localLink:umb://document/8bac09b5ee37405a9498e1494235fa01}" title="Riva">Riva</a></li>
<li>A scenic ferry transfer will take you from Garda to Riva</li>
<li>Book onto one of our included guided walks in Garda or Riva</li>
<li>Add on one of our fantastic excursions, to get even more out of your holiday (optional extras)</li>
</ul>
<h3 style="color: #00533a;"><a name="Itinerary"></a> Example Itinerary</h3>
<p><strong>Day 1: UK to Lake Garda</strong></p>
<p>Arrive into Verona airport and transfer by coach to your hotel in Garda. When you arrive at your hotel take some time to unpack before taking a stroll into Garda's centre for your first glimpse of the lake.</p>
<p><strong>Day 2: Garda</strong></p>
<p>Today’s a free day to get to know the area at your own pace. Garda combines a picturesque lakeside setting with the vibrant atmosphere of a thriving Italian community. Stroll through the busy historic centre and experience its café culture. The lakeside is full of bars and restaurants, perfect for a spot of lunch or an evening aperitivo.</p>
<p><strong>Day 3: Garda</strong></p>
<p>Garda’s well connected to all the major towns on the lake so hop on a boat to discover other nearby resorts. <a data-udi="umb://document/93a0ea3cd0334ca088eaf788bad0faba" href="/{localLink:umb://document/93a0ea3cd0334ca088eaf788bad0faba}" title="Sirmione">Sirmione’s</a> just 20 minutes away and has loads to see from castles to Roman ruins – head to the gelateria for a couple of scoops and start exploring. <a data-udi="umb://document/41229767036d47f28a27ac846e23458b" href="/{localLink:umb://document/41229767036d47f28a27ac846e23458b}" title="Verona">Verona</a> is also easy to reach by the local bus or train. You could also book onto one of our included guided walks and explore the southern landscape on foot (optional extra).</p>
<p><strong>Day 4: A day in Venice</strong></p>
<p>If you want to mix it up a bit you could book onto one of our Venice Excursions (optional extra). You’ll have around four hours of free time to explore the Basilica, the Doge's Palace and the Rialto Bridge. Or, choose to take one of the optional tours including a gondola ride or a cruise around the Lagoon.</p>
<p><strong>Day 5: Garda to Riva</strong></p>
<p>Transfer to your second centre by public ferry. The scenic journey takes a leisurely 5 hours, travelling along the length of the lake to Riva.</p>
<p><strong>Day 6: Riva</strong></p>
<p>The mild climate in Lake Garda makes for perfect grape growing conditions and you can spend today sipping some of the Veneto and Trentino region's fine wines and exploring some of what Riva has to offer.</p>
<p><strong>Day 7: Explore the Dolomites</strong></p>
<p>If you want to experience one of the most striking mountainous regions in Europe, you can book onto our Dolomites excursion for the day (optional extra). Soak up the scenery as you journey over the passes between <a data-udi="umb://document/4c9fc09241f14e3c80acb89b5c9226dd" href="/{localLink:umb://document/4c9fc09241f14e3c80acb89b5c9226dd}" title="Selva">Selva</a> and Val di Fassa. The region’s a melting pot of Austrian and Italian cultures and is known for its superb food and characterful towns.</p>
<p><strong>Days 8-11: Riva</strong></p>
<p>Spend your last few days exploring the north of Lake Garda. Walk or cycle your way from Riva to <a data-udi="umb://document/604dbba59ac64320ab6e9f1e89231a4c" href="/{localLink:umb://document/604dbba59ac64320ab6e9f1e89231a4c}" title="Limone">Limone</a> or use the bus and boat connections to get to know nearby resorts like <a data-udi="umb://document/89a5238595c34e53a5ef4c989b459fce" href="/{localLink:umb://document/89a5238595c34e53a5ef4c989b459fce}" title="Malcesine">Malcesine</a>. If you like walking, we recommend heading off on the stunning Old Ponale Road - it’s a picturesque path linking Riva and <a data-udi="umb://document/ee16f6b7f5224e5c8d9b68f1d4b62c0b" href="/{localLink:umb://document/ee16f6b7f5224e5c8d9b68f1d4b62c0b}" title="Lake Ledro">Lake Ledro</a>. Riva’s known for its water sports, especially sailing and wind surfing, so if you’re looking to get out onto the water you’ll have plenty of options.</p>
<p><strong>Day 12: Lake Garda to UK</strong></p>
<p>Transfer to the airport for your flight home.</p>
<h3 style="color: #00533a;"><a name="Includes"></a>Your holiday includes</h3>
<ul>
<li>7, 11 or 14 nights accommodation</li>
<li>A choice of accommodation in Garda and Riva</li>
<li>Return flights to Verona from the UK</li>
<li>Airport transfers by coach</li>
<li>Direct ferry transfers between resorts</li>
<li>Optional guided walks</li>
</ul>
<p><span></span><strong>Your holiday excludes:</strong></p>
<ul>
<li>Any optional extra excursions</li>
<li>Hotel city tax</li>
<li>Extras, drinks and personal expenses</li>
</ul>
<h3 style="color: #00533a;"><a name="Hotels"></a>Hotels</h3>
<p>Choose from a selection of our hotels in Garda and <a data-udi="umb://document/8bac09b5ee37405a9498e1494235fa01" href="/{localLink:umb://document/8bac09b5ee37405a9498e1494235fa01}" title="Riva">Riva</a>. Give us a call to discuss your options.</p>
<h3 style="color: #00533a;"><a name="Dates"></a>Departure dates</h3>
<ul>
<li>Wednesday or Saturday from June to mid-September</li>
</ul>
<p style="text-align: right;"><a data-udi="umb://document/74e9938fefbc44828dcfad97a456f996" href="/{localLink:umb://document/74e9938fefbc44828dcfad97a456f996}#BackToTop" title="Lake Garda Highlights" data-anchor="#BackToTop">[Back to top]</a></p>]]></description>
